{"tid":1873851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急推，今日記者會問題","createTime":"2020-02-11T01:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T01:51:26.000Z","uid":342354,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfeffcfdf9738b2310950d9afd9328f06e5ed04","tid":1873851,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"歡迎記者取材，每人只問一題逼班高官答<br />\n<br />\n1）尋晚既疏散行動中，警方防護衣明顯比前線醫護優勝，佢地係行動中分別擔當咩角色？<br />\n<br />\n2）（追問上題）承唔承認係資源錯配，醫護比警方更大機會接觸懷疑或者確診患者<br />\n<br />\n3）警方現時一共有幾多套防護衣、眼罩同n95口罩？係邊度黎？係幾時買入？<br />\n<br />\n4）相信林太(or whoever)都唔會否認，全香港人宜家都係坐埋同一條船，見住前線醫護得返一個月裝備，會唔會下行政命令警方捐贈一半醫療裝備比前線醫護<br />\n<br />\n巴絲接力, 文宣組準備"},{"pid":"8a82707f811f9111141007af5dc0ea3e3b49cd95","tid":1873851,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:15:38.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"38398746f86296c67242e06203b487ac154eacc5","tid":1873851,"uid":328463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"359ae6a648f9aa9f8ceeddd63b8c5f6ad9a4e5aa","tid":1873851,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:18:03.000Z","msg":"推呀，巴絲繼續加"},{"pid":"49309cbb71fab50c4bc51fb450c9ec40a3e6aa57","tid":1873851,"uid":105271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"點解醫護冇CSI口罩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1873824/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1873824/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ec8fde723333fcbfb6eb23d7f98b264b41fc81d8","tid":1873851,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:21:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f17cf4aa90f5e3a6c1edefc8e872a23fe6f5c6d0","tid":1873851,"uid":53695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3085d4225de0381c0db7c7cd55a